                transition: 2s;
                background-color:#299acac9;
                color:white;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <%- include ('reusables/header')%>
        <section class="mid-area">
            <div class="div1">
                <h3>What is StrathBud?</h3>
                <p> StrathBud is a comprehensive online platform designed specifically for the Strathmore University community.
                    It serves as a central hub where students can seamlessly access and manage information related to various 
                    aspects of campus life. From sports and clubs to social amenities and public relations,
                    StrathBud provides an intuitive interface that allows users to stay updated on events,
                    join activities, and access essential services. The platform also facilitates student feedback and grievances,
                    ensuring a responsive and inclusive campus environment. By integrating these diverse modules,
                    StrathBud aims to enhance the overall university experience, fostering a connected and engaged community.

                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="div2">
                <h3>How did StrathBud come about?</h3>
                <p> 
                    StrathBud was conceived as a solution to the communication challenges faced by Strathmore University. 
                    The university traditionally relied on email to disseminate information about both academic and extracurricular
                    activities. However, the sheer volume of emails led to information overload among students, causing many important
                    messages to be overlooked. This inefficacy of email communication meant that students were missing out on vital
                    opportunities and event notifications. Recognizing these issues, StrathBud was developed to provide a more 
                    engaging and user-friendly platform for sharing information. By integrating various modules that cater to 
                    sports, clubs, social amenities, public relations, and feedback, StrathBud aims to create a cohesive and interactive communication hub
                    that actively involves students and enhances their overall university experience.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="div3">
                <h3>What services does Strathbud offer?</h3>
                <p>
                    StrathBud offers a comprehensive suite of features designed to enhance the campus experience for students at Strathmore University. 
                    Key offerings include:
                    <ul class="services">
                        <li> 
                            A dedicated section for all university sports, providing information on sports leaders,
                             venues, practice days, and a sign-up form for students wishing to join.
                             It also displays upcoming sports events.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            A module with all the clubs and societies within the university, detailing their leaders, meet-up days, and venues.
                            Students can easily sign up to join their preferred clubs and societies.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            A resourceful guide to the university's restaurants, including their locations, menus, and current offers. 
                            It also covers other essential services such as health facilities and relevant announcements.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            A platform for all school announcements and events, including concerts, movies, and business fairs. 
                            Admins can upload posters and provide brief descriptions of events, ensuring the community stays informed
                            and engaged.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            A channel for students to voice their grievances and provide feedback on upcoming school projects. 
                            It includes tools for questionnaires, polls, and surveys to gather valuable student input.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
           

        </section>
        <div class="login">
            <p>WANT TO LOG IN?</p>
            <a href="/Strathbud/Login"><button>LOG IN</button></a>
        </div>
        <%- include ('reusables/footer')%>
    </body>
</html>